            "author": "Camila R.",
            "date": "Hace 3 semanas",
            "product": "Kanbae Total Alcohol Defense"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "rating": 5,
            "title": "Mi liver ahora me lo agradece",
